---
title: Wonton Shrimp Noodle Soup with Sesame-Chili Bok Choy
description: This soup is full of juicy shrimp, hearty mushrooms and springy wonton noodles. Topped with sesame chilli bok choy, dinner tonight is impressive and simple to create!
